            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">Confucius had an audience with Ji Huanzi. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">[Ji Huanzi] said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">“I have heard this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">that just a worthy can approach humaneness, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">just somebody who has approached humaneness can enact the way of the sage." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">[Confucius said:] "Now, if (you want to) approach humanity </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">and enact the way of the sage, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en">then I am not equal to it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en">how could you hope that? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en">(But) if you are not weary of granting audience to people, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en">and you are not tired of hearing about the rites, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en">then I will enjoy it for the bottom of my heart [=I can just give your concrete, modest advice] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">The master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">“If the one above does not approach humanity </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">but relies on riches, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">(why) hearing the words this forlorn man (=me)? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">The shi, is not complete in evaluating objects, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">the gentleman circulates his inspection (=inspects in all directions). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">Once the evaluation of objects is completed, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en">and virtue has not been established [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en">[...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en">being like this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en">how could one rest with him </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en">and examine and ask about what he has studied. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">First [...] follow humanity? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">The gentleman obeys it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">Huanzi said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">“If a humane person has not yet been inspected, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">his actions and behavior can be named and known? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en">The master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en">“I have heard this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en">a human person [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en">has this aspect, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.11" xml:lang="en">and has nothing with which to match it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.12" xml:lang="en">Even if he is not a humane person, then [...] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] these objects. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en">Wicked and false people, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en">also use these objects. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en">Investigating the two ways to observe the people, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en">even if there are [...] mistakes, (one) does not consider it far. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en">Huanzi said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en">“The two ways, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en">can I get to hear about them?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en">The master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en">“Words have already reached (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en">even if [...] you should not ask about it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en">then I will tell you about it.” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en">[...as for] the way of being a humane person, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en">in clothes (one) must be appropriate, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en">in demeanor (one) must not seek to be different for others, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en">not [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en">[one must] look up to Heaven and sigh, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en">saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en">“[?] not offer [?], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.9" xml:lang="en">do not taste wine and meat, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.10" xml:lang="en">[...] do not eat the five grains, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.11" xml:lang="en">choose a place [?], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.12" xml:lang="en">is it not difficult? </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en">Now as for the actions of the wicked men, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en">he loves beautiful things to make [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en">this is providing two things [=challenges?] to humane persons (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en">Now wicked and false men, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en">their abilities are many. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en">If I discuss it completely, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en">then I fear I will trouble you and make you wait for [too] long. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en">Huanzi said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en">“I am not gifted, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en">[even if] you have discussed it completely, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en">I am still troubled and do not understand it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en">what about discussing it in detail?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en">The master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en">“Wicked and false men, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en">their clothes are good [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en">they always seek to be different from the others </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] [?], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en">exalt the way [but] study excessively; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en">their words do not match their places [are not appropriate], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en">in all cases they are like their [...], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en">such are wicked people. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.6" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.7" xml:lang="en">[?] having heard [the master’s] teaching </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.8" xml:lang="en">he does not investigate and nor relies [on it]; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.9" xml:lang="en">his actions are unrespectul </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.10" xml:lang="en">and bring damage to ritual propriety [?] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] [?]. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en">Such are wicked people. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en">Their aspect is not simple, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en">when they speak they are not restrained, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en">when they appears in front of the gentleman, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en">they act with great disorder, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en">such are wicked people. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en">The gentleman makes it permanent by means of the many riches [?] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en">he prays to the four positions to move (?). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.10" xml:lang="en">The gentleman relies on what is in his command </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.11" xml:lang="en">to explore [cautiously] what he desires, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.12" xml:lang="en">he knows not to act [?] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en">[...] [?] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.2" xml:lang="en"> </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en">??? </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.4" xml:lang="en">??? to serve his superiors, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en">humanity is like this. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en">When the ones above are virtuous and wise, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en">everything will be in order. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.8" xml:lang="en">Therefore I say this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.9" xml:lang="en">that the gentleman while walking </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.10" xml:lang="en">does not show fatigue (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.11" xml:lang="en">while talking, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.12" xml:lang="en">does not show flattery, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.13" xml:lang="en">(???) </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en">Investigating this, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en">search in its midst; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en">therefore one will not be confused, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en">and the people will follow him. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en">Humane people support humanity and make progress into it [=moral, successful government?], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.6" xml:lang="en">inhumane people do not obtain to make progress into it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.7" xml:lang="en">[??] </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en">[...], </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.2" xml:lang="en">the gentleman straightens himself and establishes the shi bao </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en">to make sincere the rites and music, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.4" xml:lang="en">guides the [...] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.5" xml:lang="en">The gentleman has the way, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.6" xml:lang="en">to generate the transformation of the people [...] </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
      </body>
